lead_paragraph: Champions Barcelona came through a gruelling La Liga test at a rainswept San Mames on Sunday, beating Athletic Bilbao 1-0 thanks to Ivan Rakitic's first-half header.

headline.print_headline: Rakitic Header Earns Barca Victory in Bilbao
